@WaitingOnEngineer 

Alin, the logs are visible now. And my supposition from the previous comment was correct. The EPP client does not finish with OCR in the max waiting time (set to 9 seconds) and the file is automatically blocked. So, I say you go back to the customer and explain the situation. Again, as mentioned, this happens mostly for new files and if the customer waits a little bit, finally the file will be transferred.
